Package: HeritSeq2
Title: 
  Estimating Heritability from 
  High-Throughput Sequencing Data 
  using Generalized Linear Mixed Models
Version: 1.0.0
Authors@R: 
    person("Julius", "Olaifa", , "julius.olaifa@okstate.edu", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-3864-099X"))
Description: Provides a comprehensive toolkit to apply Generalized Linear 
    Mixed Models (GLMM) for estimating the heritability of high-throughput 
    sequencing data. This package aims to streamline the analysis of 
    large-scale sequencing datasets, enabling researchers to derive 
    meaningful genetic insights from complex genomic data.
